1
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:19,120
You were asked to drive a wedge between them,

2
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,120
but the Matriarch

3
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:22,960
wasn't happy with your performance.

4
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:42,840
Is this my father's?

5
00:00:44,399 --> 00:00:46,280
I've searched everywhere,

6
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:49,159
but it's with you.

7
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:53,159
The Matriarch wants it back.

8
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,880
I hope

9
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,799
you don't forget who you are.

10
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:00,439
You'd better behave yourself.

11
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:02,399
The one who benefits the most

12
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,239
is you.

13
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:15,959
This

14
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,200
Women's clinic

15
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,079
is of unknown origin,

16
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,519
with no official permits

17
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:20,640
or medical licenses.

18
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,560
It's clearly a scam.

19
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:23,359
Yesterday,

20
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,879
my wife came here for medicine.

21
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,120
After taking the medicine,

22
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:26,879
she vomited and nearly died.

23
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:27,920
My daughter

24
00:01:28,079 --> 00:01:29,159
took the medicine she prescribed

25
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,480
and had a high fever all night,

26
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,319
which almost damaged her brain.

27
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,319
Such a quack doctor

28
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,879
will eventually harm more people.

29
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,000
What kind of verification documents?

30
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:39,239
Who knows if they are real or fake?

31
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,680
They must be up to no good,

32
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,680
plotting against

33
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,120
the young masters!

34
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,200
Ladies,

35
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,599
your words concern lives.

36
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:50,359
Do you still have the prescriptions?

37
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:53,200
Let the authorities investigate.

38
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,079
Miss,

39
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:57,359
we've already said the patients are sick.

40
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:58,599
What more proof do you need?

41
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:00,120
Do you

42
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,480
you want me to bring him here to prove it?

43
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,200
Exactly!

44
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,879
Everyone in the Changle District knows

45
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,079
your clinic is full of problems.

46
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:07,680
Yesterday,

47
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,599
I saw someone crying, holding a medicine packet,

48
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,199
saying it was useless,

49
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,400
and caused unbearable stomach pain.

50
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,319
Sir,

51
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,680
we don't ask for anything else,

52
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,960
just a thorough investigation

53
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,599
and bring us justice.

54
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:22,120
We know your medical skills,

55
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,919
but the Minister must ensure

56
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,719
the Women's clinic complies with the law.

57
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,199
A procedure is necessary.

58
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,039
Come,

59
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,280
check the herbs and residues,

60
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,680
count the equipment,

61
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,520
and seal the prescriptions.

62
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,280
If anyone is found

63
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,400
switching herbs or tampering with records,

64
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,520
shall be detained on the spot.

65
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,919
All processes are clear,

66
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,240
the source of the medicine is clear,

67
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,400
the prescriptions are genuine,

68
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,520
the residues are preserved,

69
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,599
and the decoction is compliant.

70
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,439
The abdominal pain you reported

71
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:01,759
may be due to individual differences,

72
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,879
not the fault of the medicine,

73
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:04,120
nor the negligence of the physician.

74
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,199
The Women's clinic has treated many people.

75
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,080
It should not be slandered.

76
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,240
If we convict based on mere words,

77
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,080
what future does medicine have?

78
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,280
Today's investigation found no wrongdoing.

79
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,719
I hope you will speak carefully and investigate thoroughly,

80
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,199
and not tarnish the reputation of the clinic.

81
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,520
Wait!

82
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,719
To maintain peace in the marketplace,

83
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:27,240
we should investigate more thoroughly to ensure the clinic's actions

84
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,080
are legal and compliant.

85
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,240
Sir, if you are in such a hurry to conclude this,

86
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,240
could it be

87
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,759
that there's more to this?

88
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,719
Everything that needs to be checked has been.

89
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,240
I've heard that

90
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,599
Lady Yin frequently visits the Grand Secretariat.

91
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:41,680
Could it be that

92
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:44,439
you are colluding with them

93
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,919
to use medicine for personal gain?

94
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:46,879
How dare you!

95
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:49,719
To slander a court official and the reputation

96
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,000
and the reputation of the medical profession?

97
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,240
What punishment do you deserve?

98
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,520
Madam Yin practices medicine to benefit the world,

99
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,120
and her prescriptions are public and verifiable.

100
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,199
How can there be talk of collusion?

101
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,879
If you persist in challenging the law,

102
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,319
come with me to the court to clarify.

103
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:02,840
Sir, please forgive me.

104
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:04,199
I am just concerned

105
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:05,960
that private prescriptions are circulating

106
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,439
without official verification,

107
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,240
and treating patients

108
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,520
without proper approval

109
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,680
is like playing with people's lives.

110
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,520
As a woman,

111
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:18,720
I'm also concerned about the reputation of decent women.

112
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,920
I urge you to handle this with care.

113
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,240
A woman's reputation is everything.

114
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,199
Sir, rest assured,

115
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,480
all we use

116
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,720
is purchased through official channels,

117
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,279
Each batch is documented and traceable.

118
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,160
We are willing to provide all purchase documents

119
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:37,079
and medical records

120
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,079
for verification by the Imperial Medical Department.

121
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:39,759
A thorough investigation

122
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,199
will clear the name of the healer

123
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,639
and reassure the public.

124
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,800
In that case,

125
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,040
it's even more important to verify the use of medicines

126
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,360
against the medical records

127
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,040
to check for any adulteration

128
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,120
or

129
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,360
substandard.

130
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,439
Very well.

131
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,759
Conduct the investigation.

132
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,759
The innocent will be vindicated.

133
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:00,759
Guards,

134
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:03,279
search every unexamined area

135
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,720
thoroughly.

136
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,720
It's arsenic.

137
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,360
Arsenic?

138
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,480
Isn't that poison?

139
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,480
[Arsenic is highly toxic,]

140
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,439
[and requires official registration.]

141
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:34,399
[Private possession is a serious crime.]

142
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,040
Silence!

143
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:36,399
Madam Yin,

144
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,480
do you have anything to say?

145
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,120
This arsenic

146
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,360
doesn't belong to our institution.

147
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,680
If it did,

148
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,720
it wouldn't have been hidden in a secret compartment.

149
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,839
Someone must have planted it to frame me.

150
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:47,639
So,

151
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,240
do you have any evidence?

152
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:53,480
No.

153
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:55,959
Guards!

154
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:57,680
Seal off the Women's clinic!

155
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:00,319
Take all related personnel to the court!

156
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,120
Sir,

157
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,480
this isn't just about

158
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,160
misinformation from a merchant.

159
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:06,839
It involves the possession of poison.

160
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,160
Should we

161
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,600
hand it over to the Capital Prefecture?

162
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,839
Take them away

163
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,399
to the Capital Prefecture.

164
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:15,279
Sir,

165
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,480
this clinic

166
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,680
is run by me alone,

167
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,839
and has nothing to do with others.

168
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,560
If anyone is to be detained, it should be me.

169
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:25,839
My lord,

170
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,959
there seems to be something fishy about this clinic.

171
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,439
Should I investigate the truth?

172
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,120
No need.

173
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,959
Your wife is now in the prison.

174
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:34,040
Should we make some connections?

175
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,120
I said

176
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,319
no need.

177
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,000
Madam Yin is innocent.

178
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,160
There may be hidden truths behind Yin Shifeng's case.

179
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:40,800
Nong.

180
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:42,600
Yes.

181
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,759
My lord, you have your judgment.

182
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,560
I was

183
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,279
out of line.

184
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,600
Yin Xinyue

185
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,480
is found guilty of

186
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,120
illegally possessing banned items.

187
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,000
As there are no casualties,

188
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:54,959
according to the law,

189
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:56,360
she will receive 80 canings,

190
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,759
drugs will be confiscated,

191
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,319
her market license revoked,

192
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,720
and she'll never be allowed to practice.

193
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,079
Execute the sentence!

194
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:09,319
I have a clear conscience.

195
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,360
Heaven and earth can testify to that.

196
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,759
If the truth

197
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,399
of this matter comes to light,

198
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,319
I am an innocent person.

199
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,199
I wonder

200
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,680
how the Capital Prefecture

201
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,160
will justify itself then.

202
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,000
If you can survive this,

203
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,800
and live a good life.

204
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,319
Don't follow your father's path.

205
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:29,800
Do you know my father?

206
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,959
What happened to my father?

207
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,199
The prisoner died without regret.

208
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,879
Let her learn her lesson well.

209
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,600
Xinyue.

210
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:02,839
Xinyue.

211
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:03,439
Xinyue.

212
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,160
Xinyue, wake up.

213
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,639
Please open the cell door.

214
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:11,959
It's already a favor

215
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,600
that you're allowed to visit.

216
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,639
How did she end up like this?

217
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,800
What have you done to her?

218
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,639
She fainted after just

219
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,560
30 lashes.

220
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,879
When she recovers,

221
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:21,240
she'll get another 50.

222
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,319
She's just a woman.

223
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,680
80 lashes?

224
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:25,399
Are you trying to kill her?

225
00:08:28,959 --> 00:08:29,720
Please, my lord,

226
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,839
be more lenient.

227
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:31,759
If it's not enough,

228
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,320
I'll send someone again tomorrow.

229
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,360
Remember to bring enough money

230
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,360
when you come tomorrow.

231
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,320
Leave as soon as you finish visiting.

232
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,840
Don't drag others into this.

233
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,559
Xinyue,

234
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:52,919
we're here.

235
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:55,559
Wake up!

236
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,399
Wake up!

237
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:03,840
You're here.

238
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:09,600
I brought you some food,

239
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,440
all nourishing and healthful.

240
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,960
You must hold on.

241
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,679
We will find out the truth.

242
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,519
We'll find a way

243
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:18,840
to get you out as soon as possible.

244
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,799
Thank you, Mr. Si.

245
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,679
By the way,

246
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,399
I heard

247
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:25,879
your father is also detained here.

248
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:27,320
Have you visited him?

249
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,159
Half a month ago,

250
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,279
he was released and sent home.

251
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:31,200
I'm afraid he would cause trouble again,

252
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,200
so I've sent him back to his hometown.

253
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:35,799
Xinyue.

254
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:37,919
What's wrong?

255
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,240
I...

256
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:42,480
Sister Su,

257
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,639
when did you start

258
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,679
to be so coy with me?

259
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,000
After

260
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,639
you were detained,

261
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:53,600
I went to Mr. Xiao for help.

262
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,879
But for some reason,

263
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,639
he said your case was none of his business,

264
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,919
and kicked us out of his mansion.

265
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,720
Mind your own business.

266
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,519
Don't meddle in others' affairs.

267
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,200
Besides,

268
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,000
we have no ties.

269
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,279
Why drag him into this?

270
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,039
But if it weren't for him,

271
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,960
you wouldn't be suffering like this.

272
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,080
It really hurts.

273
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,039
This caning...

274
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,960
I'm a bit tired.

275
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,879
You should head back.

276
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:29,559
Go.

277
00:10:52,559 --> 00:10:53,200
You said

278
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,000
you would just close the clinic

279
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,000
and kick her out of the Xiao Mansion.

280
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:57,960
Why put her in prison?

281
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,080
Why drive her to the edge?

282
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,120
She's just a weak woman.

283
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:04,200
How can she withstand the prison's cruelty?

284
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:08,639
How did you become so impulsive?

285
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,240
That name is too familiar.

286
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:14,960
You should just call me Sizhanting.

287
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,759
Private possession of banned items is a serious crime.

288
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:21,159
If someone dies from it,

289
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:22,480
it's a death penalty.

290
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:25,960
If I didn't pity her innocence,

291
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,759
I wouldn't have spared her life.

292
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:29,960
You...

293
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,000
You're so cruel

294
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:35,240
just to maintain your power in the Xiao Mansion.

295
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:36,399
You're wrong, Shi'an.

296
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,440
Everything I do

297
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,720
is to clear the obstacles for you,

298
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,399
to prevent her from

299
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:44,759
hinder your future.

300
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,679
I don't need your concern,

301
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:50,200
nor do I wish to pave my way

302
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:51,879
with the suffering of innocents.

303
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:56,000
You'd better focus on the right path.

304
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,720
Don't engage in such

305
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,519
heartless schemes anymore.

306
00:12:09,639 --> 00:12:12,159
Your father taught you to be too kind.

307
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,519
However,

308
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:14,519
in this world,

309
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:16,679
kindness alone cannot ensure survival.

310
00:12:17,399 --> 00:12:18,799
You're just as foolish as he was,

311
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:20,919
clinging to loyalty and goodness,

312
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,879
ignorant of the dangers of power.

313
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:24,720
Back then,

314
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,159
if he had fought for me more,

315
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:29,840
I wouldn't have had to scheme so much.

316
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:34,399
Father lived a life of integrity,

317
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,080
never seeking power or wealth,

318
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:38,240
yet he lived with honesty and dignity.

319
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,399
What good are your far-sighted plans?

320
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,320
In the end, you're just a woman trapped in a mansion,

321
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,480
with no one truly caring for you.

322
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:49,159
You'll only end up guarding these titles and wealth alone.

323
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:50,399
How dare you!

324
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,559
All my schemes and calculations were for whom?

325
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:57,919
Back then,

326
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:00,919
I paved the way for your father to enter the IH.

327
00:13:01,279 --> 00:13:02,000
But what did he do?

328
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,120
He always put on airs,

329
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:06,360
talking about healing the world,

330
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,720
saving lives, and treating injuries.

331
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,759
and refused to get involved in palace intrigues.

332
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,360
And now,

333
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:17,120
he doesn't even have a proper tombstone.

334
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,879
His bones lie cold in a desolate grave, unvisited.

335
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:24,799
Shi'an,

336
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,759
do you want this for yourself?

337
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:29,840
Do you want your children to suffer the same fate?

338
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,159
I'm doing this for your own good.

339
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,919
I can't bear

340
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,519
the kindness of Madam.

341
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,120
I came here tonight

342
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:43,840
is not to discuss with you,

343
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,559
but to ask you

344
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,399
how to release Madam Yin.

345
00:13:58,919 --> 00:14:00,120
They are acting according to the law.

346
00:14:00,559 --> 00:14:02,240
I am just a woman trapped in a deep house.

347
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:05,279
What ability do I have to intervene in prison affairs?

348
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,519
The military officer in charge of the prison

349
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:10,000
is your brother.

350
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,879
If it weren't for him,

351
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,799
how could she have been arrested

352
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:15,360
and immediately sentenced?

353
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,039
I'm just a woman.

354
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,639
How can I control

355
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,200
my brother's actions?

356
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,679
If you want to save her,

357
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:26,000
go talk to him directly.

358
00:14:27,039 --> 00:14:27,840
Why come to me?

359
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:29,879
Ms. Sun,

360
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,240
I'm tired.

361
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:33,639
See him out.

362
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:36,279
My lord,

363
00:14:36,679 --> 00:14:37,519
please.

364
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:39,759
Remember,

365
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,279
use the back door.

366
00:14:43,799 --> 00:14:44,159
Please.

367
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:51,159
My Lord,

368
00:14:51,559 --> 00:14:52,360
Lord Si has left.

369
00:14:54,039 --> 00:14:54,679
You may leave.

370
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:56,559
I see.

371
00:14:57,639 --> 00:14:58,399
I heard

372
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,919
Lady Yin was punished with 80 strikes.

373
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:00,840
Today,

374
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:01,919
knocked out today.

375
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,159
My lord,

376
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:07,159
your hand...

377
00:15:07,639 --> 00:15:08,559
I said,

378
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:09,759
leave.

379
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:11,799
Yes.
